WEBVTT

00:10.667 --> 00:11.733
PREVIOUSLY ON THE L WORD...

00:11.767 --> 00:13.467
HE HAS, UH...

00:13.500 --> 00:15.000
ADVANCED PROSTATE CANCER,

00:15.033 --> 00:18.167
AND HE'S REFUSING ANY TREATMENT.

00:18.200 --> 00:19.467
OH, MY GOD.

00:19.500 --> 00:20.533
I'M SO SORRY.

00:20.567 --> 00:21.833
I'M SO SORRY.

00:21.867 --> 00:24.233
I WANT TO SEE OTHER PEOPLE.

00:26.733 --> 00:28.500
YOU MEAN YOU WANT TO SEE BETTE.

00:28.533 --> 00:30.600
[JENNY]: WHAT ARE YOU
GOING TO DO ABOUT CARMEN?

00:30.633 --> 00:32.567
NOTHING.

00:32.600 --> 00:34.167
I THINK
THE TWO OF YOU

00:34.200 --> 00:35.467
SHOULD BE TOGETHER.

00:35.500 --> 00:36.967
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

00:37.000 --> 00:38.700
UM, I TOLD DANA
I LOVE HER, TWICE.

00:38.733 --> 00:39.900
THAT'S GOOD.

00:39.933 --> 00:41.033
YEAH, BUT SHE DIDN'T SAY
ANYTHING BACK,

00:41.067 --> 00:42.400
AND, UM...

00:42.433 --> 00:44.333
THAT'S BAD, RIGHT?

00:44.367 --> 00:46.033
YOU AND SHANE
HAVE MADE ME A BETTER MAN.

00:46.067 --> 00:47.567
I DON'T GIVE A SHIT

00:47.600 --> 00:48.967
IF I'VE MADE YOU A BETTER MAN.

00:49.000 --> 00:52.467
IT'S NOT A FUCKING WOMAN'S JOB
TO BE CONSUMED AND INVADED

00:52.500 --> 00:53.467
AND SPAT OUT

00:53.500 --> 00:55.800
SO SOME FUCKING MAN
CAN EVOLVE.

00:55.833 --> 00:59.400
I DARE YOU TO STAY HERE
AND DEAL WITH THIS.

01:05.733 --> 01:07.167
WE'RE NOT FRIENDS.

01:12.433 --> 01:15.067
[DEEP BREATHS]

01:32.067 --> 01:33.933
[BREATHING RATE QUICKENS]

01:48.067 --> 01:50.600
HEY, VICTOR, SHE'S HERE.

01:53.633 --> 01:55.667
YEAH? SO?

01:57.633 --> 02:00.067
TRUST ME,
SHE'S A VERY SICK GIRL.

02:07.567 --> 02:13.867
* GIRLS IN TIGHT DRESSES
WHO DRAG WITH MUSTACHES *

02:13.900 --> 02:20.400
* CHICKS DRIVING FAST
INGENUES WITH LONG LASHES *

02:20.433 --> 02:26.567
* WOMEN WHO LONG, LOVE, LUST
WOMEN WHO GIVE *

02:26.600 --> 02:33.900
* THIS IS THE WAY
IT'S THE WAY THAT WE LIVE *

02:40.733 --> 02:42.333
* TALKING, LAUGHING
LOVING, BREATHING *

02:42.367 --> 02:44.333
* FIGHTING, FUCKING
CRYING, DRINKING *

02:44.367 --> 02:45.500
* WRITING, WINNING
LOSING, CHEATING *

02:45.533 --> 02:47.067
* KISSING, THINKING, DREAMING

02:47.067 --> 02:49.067
* THIS IS THE WAY...

02:49.067 --> 02:51.867
* THIS IS THE WAY
THAT WE LIVE *

02:51.900 --> 02:57.400
* IT'S THE WAY THAT WE LIVE

02:57.433 --> 03:01.167
* AND LOVE *

03:05.500 --> 03:08.133
[JENNY SINGING SOFTLY IN HEBREW]

03:17.067 --> 03:19.900
[MEN SHOUTING]

03:32.733 --> 03:36.633
[JENNY SINGING]

03:47.867 --> 03:49.167
[BETTE]: JUST RIGHT
IN THE MIDDLE

03:49.200 --> 03:50.533
OF THE LIVING ROOM.

03:50.567 --> 03:53.333
NOT A GOOD DECORATING CHOICE.

03:53.367 --> 03:54.833
YOU'RE
GOING TO BE SORRY.

03:54.867 --> 03:57.667
I JUST HAD TO GET HIM
OUT OF THE HOSPITAL.

03:57.700 --> 03:59.167
IT WAS KILLING HIM.

03:59.200 --> 04:00.667
CANCER'S KILLING HIM.

04:00.700 --> 04:01.800
GREAT. RIGHT THERE.

04:01.833 --> 04:02.900
CAN YOU GUYS
HOOK THAT UP FOR ME, PLEASE?

04:02.933 --> 04:04.067
REALLY NOT
OUR JOB, MA'AM.

04:04.100 --> 04:06.067
HERE ARE
THE INSTRUCTIONS.

04:06.067 --> 04:08.933
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TAKING ON?

04:08.967 --> 04:10.200
ARE YOU PREPARED

04:10.233 --> 04:11.900
TO WATCH OUR FATHER DIE
RIGHT HERE IN YOUR LIVING ROOM?

04:11.933 --> 04:13.700
HE COULD
GO INTO REMISSION, KIT.

04:13.733 --> 04:15.367
DON'T PUT HIM IN THE GROUND
QUITE YET.

04:15.400 --> 04:16.700
HE'S REFUSING TREATMENT.

04:16.733 --> 04:18.300
HIS DOCTORS GIVE HIM
FOUR TO SIX WEEKS.

04:18.333 --> 04:20.400
I GIVE HIM AS LONG
AS HE WANTS TO STAY ALIVE.

04:20.433 --> 04:22.367
AND WHAT ABOUT WORK?

04:22.400 --> 04:23.700
DON'T WORRY ABOUT WORK, KIT.

04:23.733 --> 04:25.700
I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
THAT DADDY'S SET UP.

04:25.733 --> 04:26.967
I'LL FIGURE SOMETHING OUT.

04:27.067 --> 04:28.067
I DON'T THINK
YOU KNOW

04:28.067 --> 04:29.700
WHAT YOU'RE IN FOR.

04:29.733 --> 04:31.067
THIS IS GOING TO EAT YOU ALIVE.

04:31.067 --> 04:32.233
I DIDN'T KNOW

04:32.267 --> 04:34.067
THAT I WOULD BE TAKING IT ON
ALL BY MYSELF.

04:34.067 --> 04:35.467
THEN YOU SHOULD HAVE
TALKED TO ME.

04:35.500 --> 04:37.767
YOU SHOULD HAVE INCLUDED ME
IN THIS HUGE DECISION YOU MADE

04:37.800 --> 04:38.900
ABOUT HOW OUR FATHER'S

04:38.933 --> 04:41.400
GOING TO LEAVE
THIS EARTH.

04:41.433 --> 04:44.900
[SINGING SOFTLY IN HEBREW]

04:49.067 --> 04:51.233
THANK YOU.

04:51.267 --> 04:52.967
THAT'S NICE.

04:53.067 --> 04:55.267
THEY'RE FROM MARK.

04:55.300 --> 04:57.900
NO, THANK YOU.

04:57.933 --> 04:59.900
LOOK, HE ASKED ME TO BRING IT.

05:01.400 --> 05:02.800
I'M NOT GOING TO
LET THE BASTARD

05:02.833 --> 05:04.067
REDEEM HIMSELF.

05:04.067 --> 05:05.467
LOOK, I DOUBT HE THINKS

05:05.500 --> 05:08.867
THAT COFFEE AND A MUFFIN'S
GOING TO REDEEM HIM.

05:19.533 --> 05:21.933
LOOK,
I HATE TO BRING THIS UP, BUT...

05:21.967 --> 05:23.633
WE HAVE RENT--

05:23.667 --> 05:25.133
NO, NO, NO. I KNOW.

05:25.167 --> 05:26.800
YOU KNOW, JEN,
I'D...

05:26.833 --> 05:27.800
I'D COVER YOU IF I COULD--

05:27.833 --> 05:28.833
NO.

05:31.067 --> 05:32.567
YOU KNOW, MARK OFFERED--

05:32.600 --> 05:34.733
NO.

05:38.433 --> 05:40.400
I'LL PAY MY OWN RENT.

05:43.100 --> 05:44.567
OKAY.

05:56.067 --> 05:57.767
[KNOCKING]

05:57.800 --> 06:00.200
COME IN.

06:00.233 --> 06:01.333
HI.

06:01.367 --> 06:03.067
OH, THANK GOD
YOU'RE HERE.

06:03.067 --> 06:05.667
CAN YOU FIGURE OUT
HOW TO HOOK THAT THING UP?

06:05.700 --> 06:07.100
OH, YEAH, SURE.

06:07.133 --> 06:08.367
IS THERE ANYWHERE
THAT I CAN...

06:08.400 --> 06:10.067
OH, THERE'S
A SPARE BEDROOM

06:10.067 --> 06:11.633
AROUND THE CORNER,
AT THE END OF THE HALLWAY.

06:11.667 --> 06:13.800
OKAY.

06:30.400 --> 06:31.633
I SEE YOU HAVE A BABY.

06:31.667 --> 06:33.933
NO, NOT YET.

06:33.967 --> 06:35.267
MAYBE.

06:35.300 --> 06:36.467
I MEAN, YES,

06:36.500 --> 06:39.167
IN 10 DAYS.

06:39.200 --> 06:40.500
MY EX.

06:40.533 --> 06:43.633
MY EX, SHE'S DUE IN 10 DAYS.

06:43.667 --> 06:45.700
YOU HAVE A LOT ON YOUR PLATE.

06:45.733 --> 06:47.167
THAT'S NOTHING NEW
TO ME.

06:47.200 --> 06:48.900
HAVE YOU THOUGHT

06:48.933 --> 06:49.967
ABOUT WHAT'S
GOING TO HAPPEN

06:50.067 --> 06:51.067
IF YOUR FATHER'S
STILL ALIVE

06:51.067 --> 06:52.100
WHEN THE BABY'S BORN?

06:52.133 --> 06:53.700
HE WILL BE.

06:53.733 --> 06:55.067
HI, JAMES. IT'S ME.

06:55.067 --> 06:57.400
CAN YOU CALL
MY FATHER'S HOUSEKEEPER

06:57.433 --> 06:58.800
AND HAVE HER SEND OUT

06:58.833 --> 07:00.200
MY FATHER'S FAMILY
PHOTOGRAPHS?

07:00.233 --> 07:01.533
JUST HAVE HER
OVERNIGHT THEM TO ME.

07:03.700 --> 07:04.767
OKAY.

07:04.800 --> 07:05.900
OKAY, GREAT.

07:05.933 --> 07:07.533
THANKS.

07:07.567 --> 07:10.433
I WAS LOOKING
AT MY FATHER'S MEDICATION CHART.

07:10.467 --> 07:12.300
WHY IS HE TAKING
PREDNISONE?

07:12.333 --> 07:13.933
ISN'T THAT SOME KIND
OF STEROID?

07:13.967 --> 07:15.767
YEAH, IT CAN HELP
WITH MENTAL CLARITY

07:15.800 --> 07:18.100
WHEN THERE'S INFLAMMATION
OR SWELLING

07:18.133 --> 07:20.600
AROUND THE BRAIN.

07:20.633 --> 07:22.900
TOWARDS THE END,
IT'LL GET VERY...

07:22.933 --> 07:25.233
CONFUSING AND FRIGHTENING,

07:25.267 --> 07:29.633
AND NOT JUST FOR THE PATIENT.

07:38.867 --> 07:40.133
TINA.

07:40.167 --> 07:41.633
DANA. ALICE.

07:41.667 --> 07:42.700
DO YOU KNOW
LEIGH OSTIN?

07:44.067 --> 07:45.433
NO. HI.

07:45.467 --> 07:47.267
OH, MY GOD.
YOU'RE SO CLOSE.

07:47.300 --> 07:48.633
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

07:48.667 --> 07:50.967
OH, HUNGRY.

07:51.067 --> 07:53.433
HEY, IS THIS
BETTE PORTER'S BABY?

07:53.467 --> 07:55.533
WELL, OUR BABY.

07:55.567 --> 07:56.233
I JUST MET HER
RECENTLY.

07:56.267 --> 07:57.233
SHE IS GREAT.

07:57.267 --> 07:58.700
DIDN'T SHE ASK YOU OUT?

08:00.467 --> 08:02.067
YEAH.

08:06.067 --> 08:08.100
UH, WE'RE GOING TO
GO SIT DOWN.

08:08.133 --> 08:09.333
YEAH. SEE YOU.

08:09.367 --> 08:10.300
OH, BUT I'LL
SEE YOU HERE

08:10.333 --> 08:11.833
LATER TONIGHT, YEAH?

08:11.867 --> 08:13.133
OH, UM, MAYBE.

08:13.167 --> 08:14.900
I JUST FEEL
LIKE A HOT BATH

08:14.933 --> 08:16.200
AND MY OWN BED
TONIGHT.

08:16.233 --> 08:18.833
WELL, WE'LL MAKE IT
AN EARLY ONE.

08:18.867 --> 08:20.067
WE'LL SEE.

08:20.067 --> 08:21.633
IT WAS NICE SEEING YOU AGAIN.

08:21.667 --> 08:23.067
YOU TOO.

08:23.067 --> 08:24.067
BYE.

08:24.067 --> 08:25.067
BYE.

08:25.067 --> 08:27.533
BYE.

08:30.667 --> 08:32.267
OKAY...

08:32.300 --> 08:34.433
SO...

08:34.467 --> 08:36.967
SO YOU'RE OKAY
WITH THAT, HUH?

08:37.067 --> 08:38.833
WHAT?

08:38.867 --> 08:41.200
WITH THAT.

08:41.233 --> 08:42.900
OH.

08:42.933 --> 08:44.467
YEAH, I'M OKAY WITH IT.

08:44.500 --> 08:46.800
I WOULDN'T BE OKAY WITH IT.

08:46.833 --> 08:48.067
I WAS WONDERING

08:48.067 --> 08:49.367
WHEN I WOULD
SEE YOU IN HERE.

08:49.400 --> 08:50.767
YOU HAVEN'T COME IN
FOR DINNER.

08:50.800 --> 08:52.333
OH, MY GOD.

08:52.367 --> 08:53.333
CAN I HAVE A HUG?

08:53.367 --> 08:53.900
YEAH.

08:53.933 --> 08:55.133
HI. WOW.

08:55.167 --> 08:56.133
LOOK AT YOU.

08:56.167 --> 08:57.267
HI.

08:57.300 --> 08:58.500
WHY DON'T YOU
SIT DOWN?

08:58.533 --> 08:59.867
YEAH, OKAY, JUST UNTIL
KIT GETS HERE.

08:59.900 --> 09:01.333
WE'RE PLANNING
A NEW LUNCH MENU.

09:01.367 --> 09:03.100
YOU WORK HERE?

09:03.133 --> 09:04.667
LUNCH. WOW.

09:04.700 --> 09:06.667
YOU'RE GOING TO BE HERE SO MUCH,

09:06.700 --> 09:07.733
AND GABBY'LL
PROBABLY BE HERE--

09:07.767 --> 09:08.833
WE'RE NOT TOGETHER.

09:12.267 --> 09:13.700
I AM SO PROUD
OF YOU.

09:13.733 --> 09:15.733
YOU CAME OUT, BIG TIME.

09:15.767 --> 09:17.067
YEAH.

09:17.067 --> 09:19.133
WELL, SORRY I DIDN'T DO IT
ANY SOONER.

09:20.967 --> 09:22.367
OH, YOU KNOW WHAT?
KIT'S HERE.

09:22.400 --> 09:24.600
I SHOULD PROBABLY GO,

09:24.633 --> 09:27.067
BUT CAN WE
HAVE DINNER?

09:27.100 --> 09:29.767
I'D LOVE TO.

09:29.800 --> 09:31.233
WOULD THAT BE OKAY WITH YOU,
BABE?

09:31.267 --> 09:33.100
OH. OH, YOU GUYS ARE...

09:33.133 --> 09:34.900
OH, MY GOD.

09:34.933 --> 09:36.200
I'M SORRY.

09:36.233 --> 09:37.767
UM...

09:37.800 --> 09:40.733
DANA, YOU DON'T HAVE TO
GET PERMISSION FROM ME

09:40.767 --> 09:41.833
TO GO OUT TO DINNER
WITH YOUR EX.

09:41.867 --> 09:43.533
YOU GUYS SHOULD BE FRIENDS.

09:43.567 --> 09:45.867
BEST, BEST FRIENDS.

09:45.900 --> 09:48.067
OKAY, WELL,
I'LL, UM...

09:48.067 --> 09:49.367
I'LL TALK TO YOU
AFTER.

09:49.400 --> 09:50.667
OKAY.
OKAY.

09:50.700 --> 09:52.133
IT WAS GOOD
TO SEE YOU GUYS.

09:52.167 --> 09:53.300
YOU TOO.

09:53.333 --> 09:54.400
OKAY.

09:54.433 --> 09:55.867
BYE.

09:55.900 --> 09:57.833
WOW.

10:00.567 --> 10:02.500
OKAY...

10:07.533 --> 10:09.233
SO, I'VE ORGANIZED HIS MEDS

10:09.267 --> 10:10.600
INTO TIMES
AND DOSAGES

10:10.633 --> 10:12.467
SO YOU CAN KEEP
TO THE SCHEDULE

10:12.500 --> 10:13.800
WHEN I'M NOT HERE,

10:13.833 --> 10:16.400
AND I'LL SHOW YOU
HOW TO CLEAN AND INSERT

10:16.433 --> 10:18.267
THE I.V. CATHETER.

10:19.933 --> 10:21.600
[STEPS CREAK]

10:21.633 --> 10:24.433
SPEAK OF THE DEVIL. HERE HE IS.

10:29.067 --> 10:30.567
WELCOME HOME, MR. PORTER.

10:32.000 --> 10:33.767
HOW ARE YOU FEELING, DADDY?

10:33.800 --> 10:35.467
WHO IS THIS WOMAN?

10:35.500 --> 10:38.067
UH, THAT'S SHELLY.

10:38.100 --> 10:39.567
SHE WAS IN THE HOSPITAL WITH YOU
YESTERDAY.

10:39.600 --> 10:40.733
YOU REMEMBER?

10:40.767 --> 10:42.833
SHE'S YOUR NURSE.

10:46.033 --> 10:48.800
AM I ON DISPLAY?

10:50.467 --> 10:52.400
CAN'T A MAN HAVE
A BIT OF PRIVACY?

10:52.433 --> 10:53.867
I SUGGEST HOSPITAL CURTAINS.

10:53.900 --> 10:55.600
I CAN ORDER THEM.

10:55.633 --> 10:57.167
CURTAINS ARE SO UGLY
AND DEPRESSING.

10:57.200 --> 10:58.733
GET SOME
OF THOSE JAPANESE SCREENS

10:58.767 --> 11:00.867
AND MAKE A ROOM
WITHIN A ROOM.

11:00.900 --> 11:03.333
HEY, WHY DON'T YOU
PICK SOME OF THOSE UP AT IKEA?

11:03.367 --> 11:05.067
UM, MAYBE YOU CAN
GET YOUR ASSISTANT

11:05.067 --> 11:06.700
TO DO THAT.

11:09.367 --> 11:10.700
SERIOUSLY, JENNY,

11:10.733 --> 11:12.400
IF YOU'RE SHORT
ON RENT THIS MONTH,

11:12.433 --> 11:13.633
IT'S NOT A PROBLEM.

11:13.667 --> 11:14.800
FUCK YOU.

11:14.833 --> 11:16.667
I DON'T EXPECT

11:16.700 --> 11:18.167
THAT IT WOULD
FIX EVERYTHING.

11:18.200 --> 11:21.300
LIKE YOU CAN BUY ME OFF
WITH MONEY AND GOOD DEEDS,

11:21.333 --> 11:24.067
LIKE I'M SOME KIND OF A WHORE.

11:24.067 --> 11:27.533
THAT'S NOT
WHAT I MEANT.

11:30.833 --> 11:31.733
[BETTE]:
I WAS PLANNING

11:31.767 --> 11:33.133
ON COMING IN
THIS AFTERNOON,

11:33.167 --> 11:34.433
BUT HE JUST SEEMED
A LITTLE DISORIENTED,

11:34.467 --> 11:36.067
SO I JUST DIDN'T
FEEL COMFORTABLE.

11:36.067 --> 11:38.067
YOU'RE DOING THE RIGHT THING,
BETTE.

11:38.067 --> 11:39.333
AFTER THIS WEEK,

11:39.367 --> 11:40.633
I SHOULD BE ABLE TO GET BACK

11:40.667 --> 11:44.067
TO SOME SEMBLANCE
OF A NORMAL SCHEDULE.

11:44.067 --> 11:46.067
LISTEN, WE DON'T WANT YOU
TO FEEL PRESSURED.

11:46.067 --> 11:47.667
YOU TAKE
HOWEVER MUCH TIME YOU NEED.

11:49.633 --> 11:50.667
THANK YOU.

11:50.700 --> 11:52.067
I APPRECIATE THAT.

11:52.100 --> 11:56.433
WE JUST NEED TO PUT
SOME STRUCTURE IN PLACE.

11:56.467 --> 12:00.600
I'M SURE THE BOARD WOULD SUPPORT
A TEMPORARY LEAVE OF ABSENCE.

12:03.067 --> 12:04.800
A LEAVE OF ABSENCE?

12:04.833 --> 12:07.367
WHAT ABOUT
THE ALAN BARNES RETROSPECTIVE?

12:07.400 --> 12:09.067
WELL, WE HAVE LEO.

12:09.100 --> 12:11.633
THINGS WON'T TOTALLY FALL APART
WHILE YOU'RE GONE.

12:11.667 --> 12:13.067
I HIRED A NURSE.

12:13.067 --> 12:16.067
I WASN'T PLANNING
ON TAKING A LEAVE OF ABSENCE.

12:16.100 --> 12:17.733
I'M SURE THAT AS SOON
AS HE TRUSTS HER--

12:17.767 --> 12:19.333
I'M SORRY
TO INTERRUPT,

12:19.367 --> 12:20.367
BUT I NEED YOUR HELP.

12:20.400 --> 12:21.367
I'M SORRY.

12:21.400 --> 12:22.500
EXCUSE ME, JUST...

12:22.533 --> 12:25.467
SURE.

12:25.500 --> 12:27.133
SO WE HAVE TO DO THIS
EVERY FEW HOURS.

12:27.167 --> 12:30.167
JUST TAKE HIS SHOULDER GENTLY,
UNDER HERE, LIKE THAT.

12:30.200 --> 12:32.133
IS THAT OKAY?

12:32.167 --> 12:34.367
[GROANS]

12:34.400 --> 12:36.533
I'M SORRY.

12:36.567 --> 12:37.700
I HAVE TO GO BACK TO THE OFFICE.

12:37.733 --> 12:39.333
JUST ONE SECOND.

12:49.433 --> 12:52.067
YOUR FATHER'S LUCKY TO HAVE YOU,
BETTE.

12:52.067 --> 12:53.733
THANKS.

12:53.767 --> 12:56.600
JUST LET ME KNOW
WHAT YOU WANT TO DO.

12:56.633 --> 12:58.700
ABOUT WHAT?

12:58.733 --> 13:01.533
ABOUT THE LEAVE OF ABSENCE.

13:01.567 --> 13:05.467
CAN I HAVE UNTIL MONDAY
TO DECIDE?

13:05.500 --> 13:06.600
OF COURSE.

13:06.633 --> 13:08.067
TAKE THE WEEKEND.

13:16.467 --> 13:18.633
[***]

13:18.667 --> 13:20.067
ASK LARA TO--

13:20.067 --> 13:22.767
IT IS LARA, ISN'T IT?
YOUR CHEF?

13:22.800 --> 13:24.100
YEAH.

13:24.133 --> 13:25.233
ASK LARA TO BRING US

13:25.267 --> 13:26.300
A SELECTION
OF SMALL TASTES,

13:26.333 --> 13:28.967
WHATEVER SHE THINKS
IS MOST DELICIOUS.

13:29.067 --> 13:31.067
YOUR CHEF.
THAT'S NICE.

13:31.100 --> 13:32.133
WOW.

13:32.167 --> 13:33.667
THIS IS MY FAVORITE
WAY TO EAT.

13:33.700 --> 13:35.700
YOU SHOULD STICK WITH ME, THEN.

13:35.733 --> 13:37.300
ALICE, IF YOU DON'T WANT ME
TO GO OUT WITH HER, JUST--

13:37.333 --> 13:38.433
I SAID IT WAS OKAY.

13:38.467 --> 13:40.833
I'M A SURVEILLANCE
PHOTOGRAPHER.

13:40.867 --> 13:42.100
I WORK
FOR DIVORCE LAWYERS,

13:42.133 --> 13:43.300
WIVES TRYING TO FIND
THEIR HUSBANDS

13:43.333 --> 13:44.300
CHEATING ON THEM,

13:44.333 --> 13:45.300
THAT KIND OF THING.

13:45.333 --> 13:46.300
THAT'S BRILLIANT.

13:46.333 --> 13:48.433
I SHOULD BRING YOU
WITH ME TO NEW YORK.

13:48.467 --> 13:50.767
YOU CAN SPY ON MY EX.

13:50.800 --> 13:52.967
[BOTH LAUGH]

13:53.067 --> 13:54.300
I'M GOING TO GO.

13:54.333 --> 13:55.567
WHY?

13:55.600 --> 13:56.967
WE HAVEN'T EVEN EATEN.

13:57.067 --> 14:00.367
I CAN'T KEEP MY EYES OPEN,
BUT PLEASE STAY.

14:00.400 --> 14:02.167
I'LL TAKE A CAB.

14:02.200 --> 14:03.500
YOU OKAY?

14:03.533 --> 14:06.600
BESIDES HAVING TO PEE
LIKE A HORSE?

14:06.633 --> 14:08.067
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

14:08.067 --> 14:09.467
HELENA, I'M TIRED.

14:09.500 --> 14:11.367
I JUST WANT TO GO HOME
AND BE ALONE.

14:11.400 --> 14:12.400
FINE.

14:14.100 --> 14:15.133
ENJOY BEING ALONE.

14:15.167 --> 14:16.700
I WILL.

14:16.733 --> 14:18.533
I WANT TO ENJOY IT WHILE I CAN.

14:21.700 --> 14:23.633
BYE, GUYS.

14:23.667 --> 14:24.833
OKAY, I'LL
SEE YOU LATER.

14:24.867 --> 14:27.633
BYE.

14:27.667 --> 14:29.433
DANA...

14:32.633 --> 14:34.567
[WHISPERING]:
YOU WON'T BE ALONE,

14:34.600 --> 14:36.267
BUT YOU'LL STILL GET LONELY.

14:42.633 --> 14:44.167
[BETTE]:
"I LOOKED UPON THE NILE

14:44.200 --> 14:45.867
"AND RAISED THE PYRAMIDS
ABOVE IT.

14:45.900 --> 14:48.533
"I HEARD THE SINGING
OF THE MISSISSIPPI

14:48.567 --> 14:51.267
"WHEN ABE LINCOLN
WENT DOWN TO NEW ORLEANS,

14:51.300 --> 14:54.833
AND I'VE SEEN ITS MUDDY BOSOM
TURN ALL GOLDEN IN THE SUNSET."

14:58.567 --> 15:02.733
"I'VE KNOWN RIVERS,
ANCIENT, DUSKY RIVERS.

15:02.767 --> 15:07.333
MY SOUL HAS GROWN DEEP,
LIKE THE RIVERS."

15:15.867 --> 15:17.767
DADDY,
IT'S TIME TO TURN YOU OVER.

15:17.800 --> 15:21.067
I'M JUST GOING TO TRY
TO DO THIS BY MYSELF, OKAY?

15:21.067 --> 15:22.067
I'M JUST GOING TO
LIFT UP...

15:22.100 --> 15:24.900
LET ME HELP YOU.

15:24.933 --> 15:27.267
IF YOU COULD JUST...

15:27.300 --> 15:29.067
TAKE THE PILLOW...

15:30.733 --> 15:34.567
AND I'LL HOLD HIS SHOULDER HERE.

15:34.600 --> 15:35.733
KIT MADE YOU DINNER.

15:35.767 --> 15:36.733
I PROMISED HER

15:36.767 --> 15:39.133
I'D MAKE YOU
SIT DOWN AND EAT IT.

15:41.833 --> 15:43.700
THAT'S GOOD.

15:52.233 --> 15:53.933
HELLO, MELVIN.

15:53.967 --> 15:56.900
IT'S TINA.

15:56.933 --> 16:00.100
"MS. KENNARD."

16:00.133 --> 16:02.967
I KNOW WHO YOU ARE.

16:03.067 --> 16:04.433
KIT'S AT WORK.

16:04.467 --> 16:06.067
SHE'LL BE HERE
AS SOON AS SHE CAN.

16:06.067 --> 16:07.433
WHO?

16:07.467 --> 16:08.667
KATIE, DADDY.

16:08.700 --> 16:10.067
SHE SAID SHE'S
GOING TO BE HERE SOON.

16:11.867 --> 16:13.533
HOW DOES SHE KNOW KATIE?

16:18.133 --> 16:20.233
I'M GOING TO GO GET YOU
A GLASS OF WATER.

16:20.267 --> 16:21.600
OKAY?

16:21.633 --> 16:24.167
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

16:24.200 --> 16:26.067
I'LL FIX YOU DINNER.

16:43.133 --> 16:44.467
I'M SORRY...

16:44.500 --> 16:47.167
IF I WAS SELFISH
THE OTHER NIGHT.

16:47.200 --> 16:48.833
IT'S OKAY.

16:56.333 --> 17:00.533
I PUT HIM IN
THE LIVING ROOM.

17:00.567 --> 17:01.633
I DIDN'T
WANT TO PUT HIM

17:01.667 --> 17:02.967
IN THE BABY'S ROOM,

17:03.067 --> 17:05.100
IN CASE...

17:17.567 --> 17:20.367
WE'VE NEVER
DONE THIS BEFORE.

17:20.400 --> 17:22.667
I'VE NEVER HELD YOU...

17:22.700 --> 17:25.133
IN FRONT OF MY FATHER.

17:25.167 --> 17:27.467
HE'S ASLEEP.

17:30.800 --> 17:33.467
NOW, THAT'S

17:33.500 --> 17:35.367
WHAT I LIKE TO SEE.

17:35.400 --> 17:37.067
NOW, PROMISE...

17:37.067 --> 17:41.300
YOU'LL TAKE GOOD CARE
OF MY GIRL.

17:46.400 --> 17:50.067
I PROMISE.

17:50.067 --> 17:52.367
AND YOU...

17:52.400 --> 17:55.367
YOU TAKE GOOD CARE
OF YOUR MOTHER TOO.

17:55.400 --> 17:58.333
YOU HEAR ME?

18:01.100 --> 18:04.233
MAXINE...

18:04.267 --> 18:06.700
DON'T RUN AWAY AGAIN.

18:09.667 --> 18:14.067
STAY WITH OUR
LITTLE GIRL.

18:14.100 --> 18:20.433
I KNOW I LET YOU DOWN,
MAXINE.

18:20.467 --> 18:23.067
I WAS WEAK.

18:25.833 --> 18:28.633
I DIDN'T MEAN TO.

18:28.667 --> 18:30.533
OH, DADDY.

18:30.567 --> 18:33.533
BUT I NEED YOU...

18:33.567 --> 18:34.967
DADDY...

18:35.067 --> 18:37.233
TO STAY...

18:37.267 --> 18:40.067
AND LOOK AFTER
MY GIRL.

18:40.067 --> 18:41.167
DADDY...

18:46.067 --> 18:48.967
[***]

18:49.067 --> 18:51.567
HEY, CARMEN CALLED ME.
IS SHE REALLY HERE?

18:51.600 --> 18:52.933
WHO?

18:52.967 --> 18:55.367
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

18:58.067 --> 19:00.833
IT'S PEACHES.
COME ON, LET'S GO.

