20:06.967 --> 20:09.133
I CAN'T FACE IT.

20:12.267 --> 20:14.633
I CAN'T FACE IT.

20:14.667 --> 20:17.033
[SOBS SOFTLY]

21:11.067 --> 21:12.900
CAN WE JUST SLEEP?

21:12.933 --> 21:15.600
YES, PLEASE.

22:05.400 --> 22:06.667
WANT SOME COFFEE?

22:53.433 --> 22:55.067
HEY.

22:57.133 --> 22:58.667
WHAT TIME
DID YOU GET HERE?

22:58.700 --> 23:01.067
A LITTLE
AFTER MIDNIGHT.

23:02.500 --> 23:04.433
HE HAD A ROUGH NIGHT.

23:04.467 --> 23:06.567
HE WAS AWAKE,

23:06.600 --> 23:08.100
BUT HE DIDN'T TALK.

23:08.133 --> 23:10.167
HE WAS IN
SO MUCH PAIN.

23:15.800 --> 23:17.467
I FEEL LIKE
HE'S GIVING UP.

23:22.900 --> 23:24.867
SHELLY'S GOING TO BE HERE
IN AN HOUR.

23:24.900 --> 23:26.133
SHE SAID SHE WANTS TO GIVE HIM

23:26.167 --> 23:27.167
A SPONGE BATH
THIS MORNING.

23:27.200 --> 23:28.167
NO, SHE WILL NOT.

23:28.200 --> 23:29.467
THAT'S AN INDIGNITY

23:29.500 --> 23:31.067
I AM NOT PREPARED
TO ENDURE.

23:31.067 --> 23:32.233
DADDY...

23:32.267 --> 23:35.200
YOU CAN HELP ME
TO THE BATHROOM.

23:35.233 --> 23:39.133
I'M PERFECTLY CAPABLE
OF BATHING MYSELF...

23:39.167 --> 23:40.333
WHICH YOU DON'T SEEM
TO BE ABLE TO DO

23:40.367 --> 23:41.300
THESE DAYS.

23:41.333 --> 23:43.133
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
OUT OF THOSE CLOTHES

23:43.167 --> 23:45.800
SINCE I FIRST ARRIVED.

23:45.833 --> 23:48.667
BECAUSE I'VE BEEN
TAKING CARE OF YOU, DADDY.

23:48.700 --> 23:51.067
TO THE DETRIMENT OF YOUR WORK,

23:51.100 --> 23:53.700
AND WHAT'S ALL THIS

23:53.733 --> 23:55.300
ABOUT TAKING
A LEAVE OF ABSENCE?

23:55.333 --> 23:56.967
I'M CONSIDERING IT.

23:57.067 --> 23:59.767
SO YOU CAN MOPE AROUND HERE
AND WATCH AN OLD MAN DIE?

23:59.800 --> 24:01.167
I WILL NOT HAVE IT.

24:01.200 --> 24:04.267
YOUR WORK IS TOO
IMPORTANT FOR THAT.

24:04.300 --> 24:06.067
IT'S NOT MORE IMPORTANT
THAN YOU.

24:06.067 --> 24:08.333
I DON'T WANT
EITHER OF YOU

24:08.367 --> 24:10.167
TO COMPROMISE
YOUR CAREERS

24:10.200 --> 24:11.933
ON MY BEHALF.

24:11.967 --> 24:14.267
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

24:14.300 --> 24:15.967
YEAH.

24:16.067 --> 24:17.300
AND YOU.

24:17.333 --> 24:18.467
IF YOU THINK BENJAMIN

24:18.500 --> 24:20.533
IS GOING TO LEAVE
HIS FAMILY FOR YOU--

24:20.567 --> 24:21.767
I DON'T, DADDY.

24:21.800 --> 24:23.833
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
YOU DON'T?

24:23.867 --> 24:26.700
I WOULDN'T DO THAT
TO ANOTHER MAN'S WIFE.

24:26.733 --> 24:29.500
IT'S HUMAN NATURE
TO PURSUE ONE'S HAPPINESS

24:29.533 --> 24:30.833
OVER SOMEONE ELSE'S MISERY.

24:30.867 --> 24:32.267
NOT ALWAYS, DADDY.

24:32.300 --> 24:33.567
AFTER HER MOTHER
STOLE YOU FROM MY MOTHER,

24:33.600 --> 24:35.433
YOU FELL IN LOVE
WITH SOMEONE ELSE, DIDN'T YOU?

24:35.467 --> 24:37.200
THAT DOESN'T MATTER.

24:39.467 --> 24:41.067
OH, UM...

24:41.067 --> 24:42.100
I'M SORRY.

24:42.133 --> 24:43.467
HELLO, TINA.

24:45.133 --> 24:46.400
HELLO, MELVIN.

24:46.433 --> 24:47.733
WHERE'S MY NURSE?

24:47.767 --> 24:51.400
I'M READY TO GET OUT
OF THIS DAMN BED.

24:51.433 --> 24:53.600
NO, DADDY, JUST RELAX.

24:53.633 --> 24:54.833
IT'S GOOD TO SEE
THAT YOU'RE FEELING BETTER.

24:54.867 --> 24:55.800
I HAVE TO GO TO WORK.

25:06.067 --> 25:08.133
JUST BE CAREFUL.

25:08.167 --> 25:09.467
ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT.

25:09.500 --> 25:12.267
OKAY, NOT TOO FAST.
OKAY.

25:15.067 --> 25:16.167
OKAY.

25:16.200 --> 25:17.667
ALL RIGHT.

25:17.700 --> 25:20.300
CAN A MAN HAVE SOME PRIVACY?

25:20.333 --> 25:21.767
HUH?

25:21.800 --> 25:23.633
YEAH, DADDY.

25:30.733 --> 25:33.700
JUST LEAVE HIM ALONE.
I THINK HE'LL BE FINE.

25:37.367 --> 25:39.433
[DOORBELL CHIMES]

25:41.067 --> 25:42.633
SORRY I'M LATE.

25:42.667 --> 25:44.067
TRAFFIC ON THE 405--

25:44.067 --> 25:45.700
WHERE'S YOUR FATHER?

25:45.733 --> 25:48.067
HE'S DOING WELL.
HE'S IN THE BATHROOM.

25:48.100 --> 25:50.333
[THUD]

25:50.367 --> 25:52.300
OH, DADDY, ARE YOU OKAY?

25:52.333 --> 25:54.600
DON'T MOVE.

25:54.633 --> 25:55.933
MR. PORTER,
DON'T MOVE.

25:55.967 --> 25:57.267
JUST TRY AND STAY
AS STILL AS POSSIBLE.

25:57.300 --> 25:58.467
NO, NO HOSPITAL.

25:58.500 --> 26:01.133
NO MORE HOSPITALS. NO.

26:01.167 --> 26:02.967
OKAY, JUST TRY
AND RELAX.

26:05.067 --> 26:06.233
WHERE WERE YOU
LAST NIGHT?

26:06.267 --> 26:07.967
YOU MISSED PEACHES.

26:13.500 --> 26:15.200
[DOOR OPENS]

26:15.233 --> 26:16.900
I NEED YOUR HELP.

26:21.733 --> 26:24.067
GOING AROUND
THE CORNER, GUYS.

26:24.067 --> 26:25.400
DADDY, ARE YOU OKAY?

26:25.433 --> 26:26.567
JUST GET HIS HEAD.
DO WE HAVE HIS HEAD?

26:26.600 --> 26:27.767
YEAH, WE'VE
GOT HIS HEAD,

26:27.800 --> 26:29.067
AND WATCH
THE IVY THERE.

26:29.100 --> 26:32.567
OKAY.
ALL RIGHT.

26:32.600 --> 26:35.167
[SHELLY]:
YOU'RE DOING REAL GOOD.

26:49.933 --> 26:51.967
WHY ARE YOU SHAVING YOUR LEGS?

26:54.200 --> 26:55.567
BECAUSE THERE'S HAIR ON THEM.

26:55.600 --> 26:58.467
SO?

27:00.533 --> 27:03.067
IS LARA GOING TO FEEL THEM
OR SOMETHING?

27:04.267 --> 27:05.233
WHAT?

27:05.267 --> 27:08.233
IT'S A LEGITIMATE QUESTION.

27:08.267 --> 27:09.567
HEY.

27:09.600 --> 27:10.633
YEAH, WE'RE JUST PICKING
A FEW THINGS UP

27:10.667 --> 27:11.900
FOR MELVIN.

27:11.933 --> 27:14.100
YEAH, WELL, LISTEN,
WHY DON'T YOU AND DANA

27:14.133 --> 27:16.167
GRAB A BOTTLE OF WINE
AND SOME FLOWERS

27:16.200 --> 27:17.567
WHEN WE HIT BETTE'S?

27:17.600 --> 27:19.200
ALL RIGHT.

27:19.233 --> 27:21.567
YEAH, SOUNDS GOOD.

27:21.600 --> 27:22.833
ALL RIGHT,
SEE YOU THEN.

27:22.867 --> 27:25.433
BYE.

27:25.467 --> 27:26.933
OH, POOR BETTE.

27:26.967 --> 27:29.600
"POOR BETTE," MAN?
POOR MELVIN.

27:29.633 --> 27:30.700
LOOK AT THIS SHIT.

27:30.733 --> 27:32.300
IT'S LIQUID FOOD.

27:32.333 --> 27:33.800
CYCLE OF LIFE.

27:33.833 --> 27:34.833
YOU WIND UP
EATING BABY FOOD,

27:34.867 --> 27:35.967
AND YOU'RE BACK
IN DIAPERS.

27:36.067 --> 27:37.233
MM.

27:37.267 --> 27:41.233
[CELLPHONE RINGS]

27:45.300 --> 27:46.700
WHO'S THAT?

27:46.733 --> 27:47.733
NO ONE.

27:47.767 --> 27:48.800
WHO'S THAT?

27:48.833 --> 27:50.300
NO ONE.

27:50.333 --> 27:51.867
IT'S LOLA.

27:51.900 --> 27:53.533
LOLA?

27:53.567 --> 27:54.967
WHO'S LOLA?

27:55.067 --> 27:57.933
UH, SHE'S THAT GIRL
FROM LAST NIGHT.

28:00.133 --> 28:02.433
WAIT, THE ONE WHO WAS
UP ON STAGE WITH PEACHES?

28:02.467 --> 28:03.567
YES.

28:03.600 --> 28:04.533
STIFFING HER
ON STAGE?

28:04.567 --> 28:05.567
SHUT UP.

28:05.600 --> 28:07.100
SHE WAS DRUNK.

28:07.133 --> 28:08.267
SHIT, IF SHE'S DRUNK,

28:08.300 --> 28:09.367
DO YOU THINK SHE'D
TEXT MESSAGE ME?

28:09.400 --> 28:10.300
SHUT THE FUCK UP.

28:10.333 --> 28:11.833
I'LL TEXT MESSAGE HER.

28:11.867 --> 28:14.367
I'VE ALREADY BEEN TRANSFERRED.

28:14.400 --> 28:15.800
ONE SECOND.

28:15.833 --> 28:17.433
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

28:17.467 --> 28:20.100
HELLO?

28:20.133 --> 28:21.633
YEAH, THIS IS BETTE PORTER.

28:21.667 --> 28:22.867
I'M TRYING TO HIRE

28:22.900 --> 28:24.533
AN ADDITIONAL
RESPITE WORKER.

28:26.600 --> 28:27.767
[SHANE]: MY DAD?

28:27.800 --> 28:30.067
INVISIBLE.

28:32.233 --> 28:34.367
BITTER.

28:34.400 --> 28:35.633
[CLEARS THROAT]

28:35.667 --> 28:37.867
DEPENDABLY SUPPORTIVE.

28:37.900 --> 28:39.800
ONE WORD.

28:39.833 --> 28:41.967
DEPENDABLE.

28:46.900 --> 28:49.467
DISTANT.

28:51.233 --> 28:52.967
[MARK]: BETTE?
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

28:54.900 --> 28:58.300
WHAT ABOUT ME? WHAT?

28:58.333 --> 28:59.733
DESCRIBE YOUR DAD. ONE WORD.

29:01.600 --> 29:03.800
DYING.

29:06.600 --> 29:08.600
THERE YOU GO.

29:08.633 --> 29:10.300
SWALLOW.

29:12.567 --> 29:13.833
HEY.

29:15.733 --> 29:16.867
I'M SORRY.

29:16.900 --> 29:18.867
MY FATHER WAS THIRSTY.

29:18.900 --> 29:21.367
MAYBE WE SHOULD LET YOU BE.

29:21.400 --> 29:23.400
YEAH.

29:23.433 --> 29:25.933
THANKS, YOU GUYS.

29:25.967 --> 29:27.633
BYE.

29:27.667 --> 29:28.933
CALL IF YOU NEED ANYTHING.

29:34.333 --> 29:35.733
OPEN.

29:38.600 --> 29:40.067
THERE YOU GO.
SWALLOW.

29:56.667 --> 29:57.667
OKAY.

29:57.700 --> 29:58.800
ALL RIGHT.

29:58.833 --> 30:00.067
I'LL SEE YOU AT 10:00.

30:00.067 --> 30:00.967
YEP. 10:00.

30:01.000 --> 30:01.967
NOW, WHAT IS IT?

30:02.000 --> 30:03.133
I DON'T KNOW.

30:03.167 --> 30:04.467
A NIGHTCLUB THING WITH JENNY.

30:04.500 --> 30:05.767
I DON'T KNOW, BUT SHE SAID
BE THERE AT 10:00,

30:05.800 --> 30:06.800
SO DON'T BE LATE.

30:06.833 --> 30:07.967
OKAY, I'LL BE THERE.

30:11.067 --> 30:12.100
ARE YOU OKAY?

30:12.133 --> 30:13.033
YES.

30:14.800 --> 30:15.867
OKAY.
OKAY.

30:15.900 --> 30:16.933
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

30:16.967 --> 30:18.533
ALRIGHTY.

30:26.167 --> 30:27.933
[QUIETLY]: GODDAMMIT.

30:27.967 --> 30:29.833
HERE ARE SOME OF YOUR THINGS,
DADDY.

30:34.433 --> 30:35.933
THERE'S ME AND MOM.

30:42.200 --> 30:44.167
I REMEMBER THAT LITTLE BALL.

30:53.367 --> 30:55.100
I DON'T REMEMBER
THIS ONE.

30:57.133 --> 30:59.000
DO YOU REMEMBER THIS?

30:59.033 --> 31:00.467
YOU AND MOM?

31:10.067 --> 31:12.100
HERE'S ME AND MOM.

31:12.133 --> 31:13.867
I HAD A LOT OF HAIR AS A KID.

31:13.900 --> 31:16.600
[LAUGHS]

31:22.300 --> 31:25.467
THERE'S SOME OF HER WATERCOLORS
IN HERE.

31:25.500 --> 31:27.267
OH, LOOK.

31:29.400 --> 31:30.967
WHERE'S THAT FROM?

31:34.633 --> 31:35.767
I...

31:35.800 --> 31:37.933
ACAPULCO, RIGHT?

31:42.067 --> 31:46.100
LET'S SEE WHAT ELSE
WE HAVE IN HERE.

31:54.400 --> 31:55.933
I THINK THIS ONE
WAS YOUR FAVORITE.

31:55.967 --> 31:58.267
WASN'T IT?

32:00.100 --> 32:03.333
SHE KNEW HER STUFF,
MOM, DIDN'T SHE?

32:09.933 --> 32:12.167
I'M GOING TO PUT THIS
RIGHT OVER HERE.

32:23.333 --> 32:25.167
I SHOULD'VE WORN
MY LATEX JUMPSUIT.

32:28.533 --> 32:30.867
I REALLY MISS
OUR FOOD ADVENTURES.

32:30.900 --> 32:32.200
YOU KNOW, THERE'S THIS
PERUVIAN RESTAURANT

32:32.233 --> 32:33.400
IN VAN NUYS

32:33.433 --> 32:34.933
I'VE BEEN
WANTING TO GO TO.

32:38.900 --> 32:40.733
I SHOULDN'T.

32:40.767 --> 32:42.700
TRAINING.

32:42.733 --> 32:44.133
NO.

32:44.167 --> 32:46.067
WELL, YEAH, SORT OF.

32:47.833 --> 32:48.833
ALICE.

32:48.867 --> 32:50.267
LARA...

32:50.300 --> 32:53.633
DANA, I'M JUST
TALKING ABOUT A DINNER.

32:53.667 --> 32:55.833
NO, THIS IS A DINNER.

32:55.867 --> 33:00.067
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT
IS A SECOND DINNER.

33:04.200 --> 33:06.700
[CELLPHONE BUZZING]

33:10.067 --> 33:11.267
HEY. HEY, IT'S ME.

33:11.300 --> 33:13.733
